% SECTION 94: BOUNDARY -- find-all with Real results
% =================================================================

[ { 3.14 } { 2.71 } ] find-all
dup 0 get 3.14 eq                         (find-all: real result 0) rt-ok
1 get 2.71 eq                             (find-all: real result 1) rt-ok  clear

