% SECTION 95: SAD -- copy-term depth limit
% =================================================================

% Build a 65-deep nested array: [[[...[ lvar ]...]]]
logic-var /x exch def
/r x def
1 1 65 { pop  1 array dup 0 r put /r exch def } for
{ r copy-term } try
/limit-check eq                           (copy-term: depth limit) rt-ok  clear

