% =================================================================

logic-var /x exch def
[
    { x 1 unify guard  { x deref 2 eq guard } naf  x deref }
    { x 2 unify guard  x deref }
] choice
1 eq                                      (naf-choice: first alt succeeds with naf) rt-ok  clear

