save /um-s2 exch def

/x logic-var def
42 /ok tag [
    [ x /ok tag  { x deref } ]
    [ x /error tag  { x deref } ]
] unify-match
42 eq                                     (um-lvar: x bound to 42) rt-ok  clear

um-s2 restore

